SIGNATURE Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned thereunto duly authorized. ALMOST FAMILY, INC. Date: March 22, 2005 By /s/ C. Steven Guenthner ------------------------- C. Steven Guenthner Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer
