Location Economics
Typical location has $1.5 million in revenue and has approximately 20% contribution margin, serving approximately 75 patients after maturing
Same store growth of 10% at mature locations
$250K - $300K investment required for start-up
We have made our last nine acquisitions at a median trailing EBITDA multiple of 4.5x
Target acquisition size: $5 to $25 million
Developing new locations to extend geographic and demographic reach
Costs are minimal; breakeven at 30 to 40 patients
