. The Purchase Price will be allocated among the Purchased Assets as set forth on
Schedule 2.4
. Sellers and Buyers agree that all tax and information returns will be prepared on a basis consistent with such allocation of the Purchase Price. The cash portion of the Purchase Price consideration shall be divided among Sellers in a manner consistent with allocations of the Purchase Price among the respective Sellers as shown on
Schedule 2.4
.
 
