Interest Calculation Date
 means three (3) Business Days following each date that Administrative Agent receives the financial statements applicable to a fiscal year and fiscal quarter of Borrower required to be delivered pursuant to Section 5.01(a) and 5.01(b), respectively, and the Compliance Certificate in each such instance pursuant to Section 5.01(c).
 
