ITEM 2.02 RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
On , Almost Family, Inc. (the Company) issued a press release announcing its financial results for the quarter ended September 30, 2012. Attached to this Current Report on Form 8-K as Exhibit 99.1 is a copy of such press release.
